This is the v5 version from the map ba_jail_experiment: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/85662


The map consists of 10 jails, a hall with activities like simon says, roulette, a pool, soccer, a first aid room, a deathtrail and secrets. 10 t spawns and 12 ct spawns.

What is new?:

Bugs fixed!!!

Deathtrail! GL

More features!
New textures!
Less light from the ball, lower ping!
Ventsdoors NOT bitable, break that!
In the poolroom are lines at one wall for spraycontest!
A highboard in the poolroom!
Teleport-Game! GL
